description: Redevelopment to provide a 15 storey building (Building 6) comprising 57 market residential flats and 62 affordable residential flats (Class C3), retail uses (Class A1/A2/A3/A4/A5), medical centre (Class D1), basement parking including 23 spaces at basement -3 level, servicing and ancillary space, highway works, new vehicular and pedestrian access and associated hard and soft landscaping.
